    "Hospitals create the record of a patient if the patient has no previous record in the system and then help the patient to encrypt and upload the EMR to the system.",
    "Third-party entities (e)Third-party entities are other hospitals, clinics, research institutions, doctors, health analysts, etc.",
    "They request permission from patients to access their EMRs through a third-party application.",
    "If the patient gives permission, they can access the data and carry out their research on it.",
    "In the proposed scheme, third-party entities are registered to the system through the application."
